    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: A Special Note from the Team at [Company Name]\n\nHi [Candidate's Name],\n\nFirst of all, thanks so much for putting your hat in the ring for our Senior DevOps role at [Company Name]. Your journey with us has been nothing short of inspiring, and we genuinely appreciate the time you dedicated to sharing your skills and passion with us.\n\nWe wanted to reach out personally to let you know that although our decision was tough, it was a necessary one. We had a very close call with a few candidates, and after much deliberation, we chose to move forward with someone who has a bit more experience with Kubernetes orchestration. We know this might be disappointing, but we want you to know that it doesn't reflect on your abilities or the potential we see in you.\n\nYour technical prowess and how well you fit into our team's culture were truly impressive. We believe that with the right opportunity, you could excel even more. We hope you won't hesitate to apply for future openings that match your strengths.\n\nThank you again for considering [Company Name]. We're grateful for the chance to get to know you, and we wish you continued success in your career journey.\n\nWarm regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name]",
